comments.content: I think it is custom drawn by a graffiti artist

I actually found it! It's a font called Sick Capital Vice and I found it on Dafont by going there to get another font and it was there on the just added page. None of the taggers that I see fonts I like use any kind of custom fonts. They are either freebies or pay fonts.
